name: Temperature.Convert

values.name: celsiusToFahrenheit
values.comment:
Converts temperature from celsius to fahrenheit.

    fahrenheitToCelsius 20 == 68

values.name: celsiusToKelvin
values.comment:
Converts temperature from celsius to kelvin.

    celsiusToKelvin 0 == 273.15

values.name: fahrenheitToCelsius
values.comment:
Converts temperature from fahrenheit to celsius.

    fahrenheitToCelsius 32 == 0

values.name: fahrenheitToKelvin
values.comment:
Converts temperature from fahrenheit to kelvin.

    fahrenheitToKelvin 23 == 268.15

values.name: kelvinToCelsius
values.comment:
Converts temperature from kelvin to celsius scale.

    kelvinToCelsius 273.15 == 0

values.name: kelvinToFahrenheit
values.comment:
Converts temperature from kelvin to fahrenheit.

    kelvinToFahrenheit 299.817 == 80
